# this is a special file that allows you to travel directly to the destination tile
# (selected by mouseover on minimap just like you would when spawning a TravelPlayer)
# but using a RaidPlayer instead of a TravelPlayer.
# the point is to fight everything on the way using RaidPlayer rules.
#
# this special file does not need any raid locations in it.
# it exists only to register an entry in the list of raids.